  "abstract": "Market access is one of the most critical linkages in farming\r\nbusiness for the rural farm households; it is also evident\r\nthat they are a prerequisite for enhancing agriculture-based\r\neconomic growth and increasing rural incomes. Rural\r\nincomes will not be substantially increased by exclusive\r\nemphasis on subsistence food crop production; rather,\r\nmore market-oriented production systems are needed.\r\nThese require intensification of agricultural production\r\nsystems, increased commercialization and specialization\r\nof production. The innovative marketing linkages through\r\ncontract farming have yielded positive results",
